preserve%22%20x=%22433%22%20y=%22204%22%20font-family=%22&#x27;Roboto&#x27;,sans-serif%22%20font-size=%2232%22%20font-weight=%22400%22%20font-style=%22normal%22%20%0A%20%3EtranslateY%28-50%25%29;%3C/text%3E%0A%3C/g%3E%0A%0A%3C/g%3E%0A%3C/svg%3E%0A" alt="HtmlToSvg.svg"></p>\n<p>The <code>top</code> property relates to the size of <code>.elem</code>\'s parent. Setting it to 50% means the top of <code>.elem</code> will be in the middle. The <code>transform</code> property relates to the size of <code>.elem</code> itself.   </p>\n<p>Therefore moving it up by 50% of its height, means the middle of <code>.elem</code> will be in the middle of its parent element.</p>\n',
